						               													<description>Legends of StormCity is a roll &amp;amp; write game, in which each player takes the role of one of the heroes of StormCity who will fight against villainous leaders and their henchmen who intend to carry out their evil plans to conquer the city.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player will control a hero sheet in which they will write down the damage they receive and the powers they can use. Villains and minions have their own game sheets.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During a game of Legends of StormCity, the villain's team activates first by rolling their dice, depending on the results they play special abilities, then try to activate their main plan and any other plans that are in play, and then initiate attacks against the heroes. Once the turn of the villains is finishes, the heroes&amp;rsquo; turn begins. Hero players take turns clockwise, starting with the player who has the initiative token. Players roll their respective dice, depending on the result heroes can activate their special abilities, deactivate enemy plans, and then attack the villains and their henchmen until they are knocked out and they can be taken to Red Cube.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the game you can assemble your own adventures, you can choose among several heroes, villains, henchmen and different plans. You can also play a campaign mode with pre-built scenarios.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;With arts by Daniel Tejerina and Alejandra Catal&amp;aacute;n.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
